examples.en: Drums are basic to African rhythm.
The piece is scored for piano, strings, and drums.
He could hear the drums before he heard the fifes.
Anyone who drums up a better way of doing this tedious task will make a fortune.
The noise of the drums pounded at our ears till we thought we would lose our hearing.
The toughs and blades of the city hoot and bang their drums, drink arak, play dice, and dance.
